description: On the first episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on their third roommate and 100 Thieves content creator, Valkyrae. They discuss Valkyrae's rise in the streaming community, the upcoming Fortnite Pro Am, FINALLY do the roommate tag, and more!
